 -- Antal Nemes <antal.nemes@quest.com>  Tue, 28 Apr 2020 08:30:27 +0200

syslog-ng (3.26.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New upstream release.
  * Remove merged in patches.
  * Update configuration version.

  [ Balazs Scheidler <bazsi77@gmail.com> ]
  * Add support for the snmp() destination (syslog-ng-mod-snmp package).
  * Move the http() destination into a separate package (syslog-ng-mod-http).
  * Move BSD process accounting (pacct) support into the core package.
  * Move tags-parser() to the core package.
  * Add support for librdkafka based kafka destination (in mod-rdkafka
    package).
  * Use upstream scl.conf .

 -- Laszlo Boszormenyi (GCS) <gcs@debian.org>  Sun, 08 Mar 2020 14:18:20 +0000

